\_def\_readverbline #1^^J{%
   \_def\_tmpa{\_empty#1}%
   \_let\_next=\_readverbline
   \_ea\_isinlist\_ea\_tmpa\_ea{\_Doc}\_iftrue \_let\_next=\_processinput \_fi
