   and `\_tmpb` is the name to be printed. See \^`\_makecsF` above and the
   example at the beginning of this section.
   \_cod -----------------------------

\_def\_intlink{\_link[cs:\_tmpa]{\Blue}{\_csstring\\\_tmpb}}

